          "content_hash": "7133afb701175e24",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "ZJU, Jiwei Li"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "f3754e7132f9c4ba",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "这人到底在ZJU吗? 之前也是听说口碑烂完了。蹲一下"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "0000000000000000",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "0000000000000000",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "30ac7301e54683b0",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "USTC, Yan Song"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "c3dba9b9658c6475",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "这人坑过多少学生就不用说了吧？从深圳一路坑过来。当年在深圳干的那些事情不知道还有多少人记得。(展开说说?)"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "c8b41226c59e68cb",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "逆天，避雷避雷"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "0000000000000000",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "43fcb961c4cbd40a",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "USTC,"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "13dc8a0f70034b06",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": " Xiang-Yang Li"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "992e1f2e822019e9",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "实验室强制打卡，组会骂人】"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "62b049c8c362be28",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "我本科在李老师组里待过很长时间，后来出国了，个人感觉他人确实还挺好，甚至手把手教函数加密。听有学长说还帮忙debug过code~（nsnmn，我们这一届lxy的学生，所有的签字全部拖到最后一刻，并且经常以不做xx就不给签字来威胁）"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "8cf48a8296592210",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "沽名钓誉之辈，去这个组只能说这辈子有了"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "0000000000000000",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "870966a1b1edf1b9",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "USTC, Jie Wang"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "986ffdd3c3049410",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "Intern本科生养鱼，maybe只care少院同学吧，完全不给指导啊，也没人带你hhh"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "8b59bef57cc45395",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "少院的也不在乎啊，奈何取之尽锱铢，用之如泥沙"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "77c14be707c9c69f",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "苦一苦学生，骂名我来当"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "fb3805400a34b5f0",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "生命会找到自己的出路"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "4f5f182d3a605b9b",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "无论你上辈子造了什么孽，来了这里哪怕一天，你都连本带利还清了"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "c5bd3985830177d4",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "在这里毕业不只有欣喜还有解脱，当代塞拉斯"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "195b25a04d13eddf",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "永别了牢笼"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "ed6cffa6d3f77c8e",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "看《活着》像看爽文"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "0000000000000000",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "a798f0b17648a922",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "妈妈 我将变成萤火虫"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "3315de5da5b22328",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "童年 · 在人间 · 我的奋斗"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "e18426b41d2c6a6f",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "实验室的存在证明了一件事，学生们从不低贱，没有导师指导没有科研资源，学生们一样可以创造出伟大的成就"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "e441f7f140179fea",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "组里不让私下实习。本科硕士走组里的合作实习，工资要上交，连房补都没有。"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "6b164335accde115",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "30号左右人的大组，一个博后都没有，没有小老板，导师不懂前沿，博士都想着压榨硕士发文章。"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "0000000000000000",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "08b056e43483ad6d",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "USTC, Yu Zhang"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "aa1b9c97f412006d",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "读博期间经常被骂，看到她就感觉心情很不好，组内全是垃圾横向，只想赚钱，对学生毫无指导，高年级博士无论文延毕成常态了。"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "f93b8e99556fae19",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "我是张老师几年前毕业的学生，那个时候实验室人很少，就读体验还行。"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "0000000000000000",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "a7bf41e1b5505f85",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "CSU, Xu Su(是 xiu su吗...)"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "5d1d675eeb77af94",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "经典npd，不顺他的意或者做的不好就会一直否定你。"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "ba6165f241b34f03",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "让保研生暑假打了几个月工，说99%可以拿offer。结果被鸽"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "0000000000000000",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "ee77a4244176a76a",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "CSU, 可视化夫妻店"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "b3974e63932343c1",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "横向多到做不完"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "66bc86f8395fbc1e",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "教授抢PhD一作，PhD抢本科生一作"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "0000000000000000",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "5a714fee82be3c48",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "Westlake, Ziqing Li（请称呼他为stan Li）"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "b6299e4957288754",
